OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy with overnight rain quickly
OL,7,Fclearing to leave mostly dry and
OL,8,Fbright conditions on Thursday.
OL,9,FBecoming unsettled with some rain at
OL,10,Ftimes Friday and Saturday. Often windy
OL,11,Fand relatively mild.
